Class OntologyConcept_Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • TOP_Type
      • org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.refsem.OntologyConcept_Type
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UmlsConcept_Type

    public class OntologyConcept_Type
extends TOP_Type
    Ontologies (e.g., SNOMED-CT) provide an expert semantic representation for concepts. They typically assign a code to a concept and normalize across various textual representations of that concept. IdentifiedAnnotation and Elements may point to these normalized concept representations to indicate clinical concepts. Equivalent to cTAKES: edu.mayo.bmi.uima.core.type.OntologyConcept Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015
